JOGL Debug Module

This module adds a new item to the Wonderland Tools menu to display debug information about your OpenGL graphics environment. This information may be useful for developers when debugging graphics related exceptions.

Instructions:
1) Build the module and insert it according to normal procedures.
2) Go to View->OpenGL Debug
3) View the availability of JOGL capabilities. Ctrl+C to copy them.


Issues:
It doesn't work until the client has finished logging in.

